description:
Golden Tiger Eclipse, Jade Hare Prosperity is the 2023 edition of Li Xi: an [Endproject](https://endproject.xn--mk1bu44c) endeavor.  
  
Happiness is in action, not just in possession.  
You cannot make yourself happy by depriving others of happiness.  
  
Smiling makes a person more beautiful and cheerful, and it costs nothing.  
Being selfless is true and real.  
  
Love is care.  
Give generously to happiness and be happier yourself.
name: Li Xi
